{"tid":2382041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"脫單夢碎！替正妹贖身被狠咬一口　痴情男54萬飛了","createTime":"2021-01-27T04:31:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-27T05:31:43.000Z","uid":87428,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6e96a063a699a2045e8e1cc8aa4bbec555dda037","tid":2382041,"uid":87428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T04:31:34.000Z","msg":"家住北市的張姓網路遊戲工程師（30歲）去年7月，在交友軟體認識自稱「陳喬安Amy」的直播主，Amy以交往為誘餌，設下愛情陷阱，她不斷對張男灌迷湯「希望兩人能一路走下去」。張男以為找到真愛，不僅在直播平台「斗內」Amy，還出錢替她解除直播主合約，最後Amy人間蒸發，張男發現美夢成空，反被騙光54萬積蓄。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/FzSsN_3EhxtDlmS8EunkS-nfORE=/1170x869/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OIKWJYI5XNF57IW2X2RYOJR3QI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFzSsN_3EhxtDlmS8EunkS-nfORE%3D%2F1170x869%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOIKWJYI5XNF57IW2X2RYOJR3QI.jpg&h=8366785c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n張姓網路遊戲工程師因工作繁忙，遲遲沒有交到女友，於是他透過交友軟體，希望可以找到心儀的對象。去年7月，名叫「陳喬安Amy」的女孩私訊張男，她自稱是直播平台的直播主，他們倆相談甚歡，幾天後便轉往直播平台繼續聊天。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/Z4AiDp4pPO53hXziWz42C8tsPpk=/190x338/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VI5BHERTORDDHA54UJP6YTTTOQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZ4AiDp4pPO53hXziWz42C8tsPpk%3D%2F190x338%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVI5BHERTORDDHA54UJP6YTTTOQ.jpg&h=225f9c4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nAmy不斷向張男灌迷湯，稱未來以交往為前提，「希望兩人能一路走下去」。他們天天聊天，愈聊愈投機、契合，張男以為找到真愛，終於可以脫單。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/7rQQGYAAzheJp-GSAPnODz2H58k=/370x482/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KY5AZJ5TT5AJNK7Q652RCGKY3A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7rQQGYAAzheJp-GSAPnODz2H58k%3D%2F370x482%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKY5AZJ5TT5AJNK7Q652RCGKY3A.jpg&h=2be2efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n從張男提供的照片可以看出，Amy身材高挑纖瘦、外型亮麗、皮膚白皙，還有一雙水汪汪的大眼。張男描述，她的個性外向活潑，講話還帶點娃娃音，不時還會撒撒嬌，「對她的確很著迷，因此很快就暈船了。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/bdwScSaLOPvWQXzI7qm6_RPc23g=/371x858/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BDQVNZOZJFG5ZCL2QNMPYZQMRE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FbdwScSaLOPvWQXzI7qm6_RPc23g%3D%2F371x858%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBDQVNZOZJFG5ZCL2QNMPYZQMRE.jpg&h=7020a8b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAmy稱自己是新主播，希望張透過直播平台，送1000元虛擬禮物當作告白的見面禮。Amy對張男畫了多大餅，「我希望今天可以收到這個禮物，手牽著手一起邁向下一個一年」、「我也希望讓大家知道你的存在比任何人來的重要，也代表我在你心中是有那個份量」。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/local/20210124/3LTCJH3DWVCGNDJEHIO2ISK7MI/?utm_campaign=twad_social_appledaily.tw&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;s=facebook&amp;utm_content=video_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3A-99390F8U0RmtboFnk32kKOSftqWda1hBOAdH4_4eCvjxalfTQrCX5E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210124%2F3LTCJH3DWVCGNDJEHIO2ISK7MI%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_appledaily.tw%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26s%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dvideo_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3A-99390F8U0RmtboFnk32kKOSftqWda1hBOAdH4_4eCvjxalfTQrCX5E&d=vmCIlZEHEchodQF1AoZdn8sFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=ffb93ccd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210124%2F3LTCJH3DWVCGNDJEHIO2ISK7MI%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_appledaily.tw%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26s%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dvideo_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3A-99390F8U0RmtboFnk32kKOSftqWda1hBOAdH4_4eCvjxalfTQrCX5E&h=4cd6f7f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/local/20210124/3LTCJH3DWVCGNDJEHIO2ISK7MI/?utm_campaign=twad_social_appledaily.tw&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;s=facebook&amp;utm_content=video_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3A-99390F8U0RmtboFnk32kKOSftqWda1hBOAdH4_4eCvjxalfTQrCX5E</a>"},{"pid":"4dcfe3af216f7bf295907a44ee52f94c1ba94fe4","tid":2382041,"uid":133183,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T04:33:34.000Z","msg":"明明好sad 睇到啲chat record又有啲好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"495ccdc6211677cb5623f79d6059e781b8ba1f04","tid":2382041,"uid":83654,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T04:35:48.000Z","msg":"on9 仔， 54萬 屌足成個月外送茶"},{"pid":"d653a05ead6eb0606ca3644012a8a48e9cae06b6","tid":2382041,"uid":209890,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T04:36:35.000Z","msg":"搵佢出黎唔難啦<br />\n台灣分分鐘可以反告條女"},{"pid":"6901d7e1a9dc0c6e4f0d58ae0ce3c4b1846c0131","tid":2382041,"uid":68081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"495ccdc6211677cb5623f79d6059e781b8ba1f04","tid":2382041,"uid":83654,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T04:35:48.000Z","msg":"on9 仔， 54萬 屌足成個月外送茶"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T04:42:41.000Z","msg":"你太膚淺，識玩一定係玩一個男人屎忽！深不見底<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dc2a6d815dba34c63b03f8335db3c3f6b926e6b","tid":2382041,"uid":7365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T04:45:38.000Z","msg":"張姓網路遊戲工程師因工作繁忙，遲遲沒有交到女友<br />\n<br />\n真係因為咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ef9f1533efb3fba5b0faccb7678af960ba050bc","tid":2382041,"uid":128705,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T05:31:43.000Z","msg":"對話另一邊係個阿叔黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n桃色陷阱根本周圍都有<br />\n50幾萬台幣當交學費啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}